                <div class="rendering rendering_researchoutput  rendering_researchoutput_standard rendering_contributiontojournal rendering_standard rendering_contributiontojournal_standard"><a rel="ContributionToJournal" href="https://research.birmingham.ac.uk/en/publications/the-association-between-type-2-diabetes-mellitus-hip-fracture-and/" class="link"><span><strong>The association between type 2 diabetes mellitus, hip fracture, and post-hip fracture mortality: a multi-state cohort analysis.</strong></span></a> / Tebé, C.; Martínez-Laguna, D.; Carbonell-Abella, C. et al. <br />In: <a rel="Journal" href="#" class="link"><span>Osteoporosis International</span></a>, Vol. 30, No. 12, 01.12.2019, p. 2407-2415.<p class="type"><span class="type_family">Research output<span class="type_family_sep">: </span></span><span class="type_classification_parent">Contribution to journal<span class="type_parent_sep"> › </span></span><span class="type_classification">Article</span><span class="type_classification"><span class="type_parent_sep"> › </span>peer-review</span></p></div>
